    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in 'fair' condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the roof and hood. Mechanically, the car runs and drives well, but the suspension is starting to feel a bit loose, and the interior shows significant wear on the driver's seat and floor mats. It\u2019s a solid option for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind a few cosmetic and mechanical imperfections.",
